EmailTemplate.subject: Senior College Tour
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
It's unfortunate that you were unable to come along on our recent Senior College Tour.
If you would like to visit the School, you are most welcome to come along on a Head of School tour. We run the tours regularly throughout the school term and it's a great opportunity to tour the facilities and meet our staff and students. You can book directly into a tour on a date that suits you via our website www.sacs.nsw.edu.au.
For those of you who have enrolled, welcome to St Andrew's and we look forward to you joining our Senior College next year.
If you are considering enrolment, our Enrolments staff are happy to assist you with your application or any queries you may have. You can contact the Enrolments team on 9286 9500.
In the meantime, attached below are some links with information on Senior College at St Andrew's that provide further insight into our community and cohort.
I look forward to the opportunity to welcome your family next time at St Andrews Cathedral School.
Regards
Bruce Perry Registrar/Mathematics Teacher
St Andrew's Cathedral School
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia direct +61 2 9286 9507 mobile 0418 255 923 email BPerry@sacs.nsw.edu.au phone +61 2 9286 9500 fax +61 29286 9550
